      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. It\u2019s super clean, runs perfectly, and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
