    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its original showroom depth and clarity; there are no swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections to be found. The interior is equally pristine, featuring supple, uncreased leather, original protective floor mats, and a cabin that remains smoke-free and scent-neutral. Every electronic component and mechanical system functions with factory precision. The sale includes a comprehensive binder of all service records from new, documenting a recent major preventative maintenance cycle and a professional ceramic coating application. This is a rare, turn-key opportunity for a discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection.",
